      "hottest_planet_due_to_runaway_greenhou": "Hottest planet due to runaway greenhouse effect. Rotates backwards!",
      "only_known_planet_with_liquid_water_an": "Only known planet with liquid water and life.",
      "has_the_tallest_volcano_in_the_solar_s": "Has the tallest volcano in the solar system: Olympus Mons (21.9 km high).",
