      "educational_concepts": "💡 Educational Concepts",
      "color_theory_additive_vs_subtractive_m": "Color theory (additive vs subtractive mixing, complementary colors, HSL/RGB), mathematical curves (hypotrochoids, Lissajous), fractals & self-similarity, cellular automata & emergence, tessellation geometry, op art visual perception, WCAG accessibility standards, and computational art. Every tool teaches the math behind the beauty.",
