      "i_can_explain_why_this_profile_yields_": "I can explain why this profile yields this energy state.",
      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Explain in your own words...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Inquiry widget — no score, no reveal, no answer dump. Energy model is illustrative (drag ∝ m^0.67 / wingspan). V-formation savings vary ~10–30% across species and positions (Lissaman & Shollenberger 1970 theoretical upper bound; in-flight measurements include Weimerskirch et al. 2001 on pelicans and Portugal et al. 2014 on ibises). Widget uses 22% as a midpoint estimate. For real-world stopover ecology consult primary literature.",
