      "patella_patellofemoral_joint": "Patella / patellofemoral joint",
      "patellofemoral_pain_syndrome_occurs_wh": "Patellofemoral pain syndrome occurs when the patella does not track smoothly in its groove on the femur. Repeated stress from running causes cartilage irritation. Treatment includes quad strengthening, hip stabilization, and activity modification.",
      "the_shoulder_that_won_t_lift": "The Shoulder That Won't Lift",
