      "the_trachea_splits_into_left_and_right": "The trachea splits into left and right main bronchi, each entering a lung. They branch into smaller bronchioles.",
      "alveoli_2": "Alveoli",
      "300_million_grape_like_sacs_where_gas_": "300 million grape-like sacs where gas exchange occurs. O2 diffuses into blood; CO2 diffuses out. Surface area equals a tennis court.",
