      "octopuses_are_mid_trophic_consumers_in": "Octopuses are MID-TROPHIC consumers in a coral reef food web. Which of the following best supports this?",
      "they_eat_crabs_fish_clams_and_are_eate": "They eat crabs + fish + clams AND are eaten by sharks + groupers + sea otters",
