      "visit_a_bleached_coral_region": "Visit a bleached coral region.",
      "global_mass_coral_bleaching_events_occ": "Global mass coral bleaching events occurred in 1998, 2002, 2010, 2014-17, 2020, and 2023-24. Each event has killed 20-50% of affected reefs. Octopuses lose den structure and prey base when reefs collapse.",
