      "not_just_consumers_of_information_stud": ", not just consumers of information. Students should leave each session having generated their own data, made their own observations, and built their own explanations from evidence — not just memorized vocabulary.",
      "the_community": "👥 The community",
      "cephalopod_biology_is_a_small_collabor": "Cephalopod biology is a small, collaborative field. Most active researchers number in the hundreds globally. The community spans university labs, marine stations (Woods Hole MBL, MBARI, AZTI in Spain), aquariums, and museum curators. Many of these scientists have explicitly written about animal welfare, citizen science, and increasing field accessibility — the kind of values that aligned with this tool's UDL design.",
