      "why_this_matters_3": "⏳ Why this matters",
      "octopus_lifespans_are_short_1_2_years_": "Octopus lifespans are SHORT — 1-2 years for most species, with the FINAL phase being a dramatic genetically programmed self-destruct after reproduction. Understanding this cycle is the key to ",
      "why_octopuses_can_t_be_domesticated_li": "why octopuses can't be domesticated like dogs",
