      "these_discoveries_demonstrate_that_cep": "These discoveries demonstrate that cephalopod biology is NOT a closed book. Each year, new findings reshape our understanding of cephalopod cognition, sensory systems, evolution, and welfare implications. Citizen science contributions + AI-assisted analysis + new imaging technologies are expanding what's possible.",
