      "daphne_major_1977": "Daphne Major, 1977",
      "peter_rosemary_grant_tagged_every_medi": "Peter & Rosemary Grant tagged every medium ground finch on this Galápagos islet for 40+ years. In 1977 a severe drought killed 85% of small soft seeds. The next year, surviving birds had measurably larger beaks — observed evolution within ONE generation.",
      "year": "Year",
