      "bars_get_taller_slower_as_the_prey_bec": "Bars get TALLER (slower) as the prey become better camouflaged.",
      "predator_vision_lab": "Predator Vision Lab",
      "click_prey_to_eat_them_each_round_the_": "Click prey to \"eat\" them. Each round, the survivors reproduce — and each generation looks slightly more like the background. By round 10, the prey will be almost invisible. The camouflage you're watching emerge is YOUR doing — you applied the selection pressure that produced it.",
      "round_2": "Round",
