      "epilepsy_foundation": "Epilepsy Foundation",
      "where_community_preference_is_mixed_e_": ". Where community preference is mixed (e.g. person-first vs identity-first language), this module follows the most common preference and notes it.",
      "pick_a_section_above_each_section_is_s": "Pick a section above. Each section is short — these are the things most adults don’t know either.",
      "get_their_attention_visually": "Get their attention visually: ",
      "wave_in_their_line_of_sight_tap_their_": "wave in their line of sight, tap their shoulder. Don’t grab. Don’t shout — louder doesn’t help.",
      "face_them_directly": "Face them directly",
      "so_they_can_see_your_mouth_and_express": " so they can see your mouth and expressions. Good lighting on your face. Don’t cover your mouth.",
