      "the_danger_zone_fda_food_code": "🌡️ The Danger Zone (FDA Food Code)",
      "bacteria_grow_fastest_between_40_f_and": "Bacteria grow fastest between 40°F and 140°F (4°C–60°C). This is \"the danger zone.\" Food shouldn't sit here for more than 2 hours total (1 hour if it's over 90°F outside). Drag the slider to see what happens at different temps.",
      "food_temperature": "Food temperature",
